Name: annotated_types
URL: https://github.com/annotated-types/annotated-types
Revision: 0735cd3d4c272b88405b6b04009716b691115210
Version: v0.7.0
License: MIT
License File: src/LICENSE
Description: This package provides metadata objects which can be used to represent common
constraints such as upper and lower bounds on scalar values and collection sizes, a Predicate marker
for runtime checks, and descriptions of how we intend these metadata to be interpreted.

Upgrading the version of annotated_types is done by bumping the version of pydantic in
//manifests/third_party/pylibs/requirements.in and then running
////manifests/third_party/pylibs/update-pylibs.sh.
